### My Pixel

An Espruino Pixel like device which used a ST7302 always on Display. 

![](Mypixel.jpg)

Holding down the rightmost button displays a menu from which applications are selected. An Espruino file appears in the application menu if it has a name of the form `name.app.js`.

The device has a small piezo speaker for sounding alarms etc.

The monitor application accesses data from CO2 Monitors.
 